<% layout('./layouts/boilerplate') %>
<body>

    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What is the purpose of this website?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">This website is designed to provide users with detailed answers to commonly asked questions about our services, products, or other related topics.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How can I contact customer support?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">You can reach customer support by emailing us at support@example.com or by calling our helpline at 1-800-123-4567.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What payment methods do you accept?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">We accept credit cards, debit cards, PayPal, and bank transfers. We are working on integrating additional payment methods soon!</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Do you offer international shipping?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we ship our products worldwide. Shipping charges may vary depending on your location and the size of the order.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What is your return policy?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">We offer a 30-day return policy on most items. The product must be in its original condition, and a proof of purchase is required. For more details, please visit our Return Policy page.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How can I reset my password?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">To reset your password, click on the 'Forgot Password' link on the login page. Enter your registered email, and we’ll send you a password reset link.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I track my order?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. Use this number to track your order on our website.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Are there any discounts for bulk purchases?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer discounts for bulk purchases. Please contact our sales team for more details on pricing and offers.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What browsers are supported by this website?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Our website supports all major browsers, including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge, and Opera. For the best experience, please ensure your browser is updated to the latest version.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How can I unsubscribe from the newsletter?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">You can unsubscribe from our newsletter by clicking the 'Unsubscribe' link at the bottom of any email we send you.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How do I create an account?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Click on the 'Sign Up' button at the top-right corner of the homepage. Fill out the registration form with your details and submit it. You will receive a confirmation email to activate your account.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I update my account details?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can update your account details by navigating to the 'My Account' section after logging in. Here, you can update your personal information, password, and preferences.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How can I cancel my order?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">You can cancel your order by visiting the 'My Orders' section of your account and selecting the order you wish to cancel. Please note that orders can only be canceled before they are shipped.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Do you provide a warranty on your products?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer a warranty on most of our products. The warranty period and terms vary depending on the product. Please refer to the product details for specific warranty information.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Is my payment information secure?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we use industry-standard encryption to ensure that your payment details are safe and secure. Your data is handled with the utmost confidentiality.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What is your delivery time?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Delivery times vary depending on your location and the product. Typically, orders are delivered within 3-7 business days. You can track your order for more accurate delivery estimates.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I change my shipping address after placing an order?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can change your shipping address as long as your order hasn’t been shipped. Please contact customer support to update your shipping details.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Do you offer gift wrapping services?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer gift wrapping services for select products. You can select the gift wrapping option during the checkout process.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What should I do if I receive a damaged product?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">If you receive a damaged product, please contact our customer support team within 48 hours of receiving the item. Provide details and photos of the damage for assistance with a replacement or refund.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I subscribe to product updates?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can subscribe to product updates by signing up for our newsletter or enabling notifications in your account settings. We’ll keep you informed about new arrivals, promotions, and updates.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How do I apply a discount code?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">During the checkout process, enter your discount code in the designated field and click 'Apply.' The discount will be reflected in your total amount if the code is valid.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Do you have a mobile app?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, our mobile app is available for download on the App Store and Google Play. It provides a seamless shopping experience and exclusive app-only deals.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I leave a review for a product?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can leave a review for a product by visiting the product page and clicking on the 'Write a Review' button. We appreciate your feedback!</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What happens if I forget to log out of my account?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">If you forget to log out, your session will expire automatically after a certain period of inactivity for security purposes. Always remember to log out if you’re using a shared device.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

